## Credential / secret drift warning

The STAG failure-callback node uses `$vars.N8N_INGEST_SECRET` (n8n) and the app validates it
against `N8N_INGEST_SECRET` (`.env.local` line ~70). If the two drift, the callback will 401 and
the only remaining success signal is the DB trigger `trg_outreach_queue_n8n_success`. Keep these
in sync when rotating secrets.
